{"tid":1690583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【快 點 強】 30歲英國性愛成癮女人 自曝用社交軟體輕鬆達成「百人斬」","createTime":"2019-11-03T11:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:59:06.000Z","uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bd44baea5c5982b22509c68283d425b81919ace5","tid":1690583,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國有位女子勞麗（Laurie Jade Woodruff）近日對媒體自曝是「性愛成癮的女人」，從12歲失去童貞後，長年沉浸於雲雨之歡，對此，她還透露，自己透過社交軟體IG與100位以上的陌生人發生過親密關係。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，現年30歲的英國女子勞麗向《太陽報》爆料，自己是一位「性成癮患者」，打從12歲拋棄「第一次」後，她已透過Instagram與100至200位陌生人滾過床單，勞麗表示，「過去最荒唐的時期，我沉溺在跟陌生人上床的快感，社群媒體讓這種事變得異常容易，我不用去酒吧或使用付費的約會軟體，Instagram能幫我在幾分鐘內約到床伴」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gazeta-shqip.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/5c84df8166a97cfe3fdb9175.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gazeta-shqip.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F5c84df8166a97cfe3fdb9175.jpg&h=040f9670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據外媒報導，由於過去約床伴曾多次讓自己陷入危險之中，勞麗回顧過去的荒唐經歷深感恐懼和空虛，在參加戒除成癮康復團體後，勞麗目前已能夠控制性癮症狀，此外，她也將自己的過往經驗出版成書，以幫助有相同困擾的人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.ladbible.com/thumbnail?type=jpeg&amp;url=http://beta.ems.ladbiblegroup.com/s3/content/a4cd00905dbc8de2cf2d06cda3bdbcca.png&amp;quality=70&amp;width=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ladbible.com%2Fthumbnail%3Ftype%3Djpeg%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fbeta.ems.ladbiblegroup.com%2Fs3%2Fcontent%2Fa4cd00905dbc8de2cf2d06cda3bdbcca.png%26quality%3D70%26width%3D720&h=c215e087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f619ba327f449ae8d9cfed83bff60587f369c75","tid":1690583,"uid":230239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"絕對有講過"},{"pid":"6b5a3c4ea55ca9d8f14de772063b54651489c85d","tid":1690583,"uid":8113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"這些機會 ..."},{"pid":"a57da1bfa1b2f27a682191e75c7c73eb38710251","tid":1690583,"uid":161190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":